Description: Men’s Therapy Center is a mental health platform for men to start expert evidence-based individual therapy.
Full Description: Welcome to the Men's Therapy Center, where we're dedicated to empowering men to take control of their mental health. Our online platform connects modern men with licensed mental health professionals who specialize in evidence-based therapy for a range of life problems including unexpected career transitions, anxiety, relationship problems, work stress, low self-esteem, addiction, performance difficulties, procrastination, anger, trauma, ADHD, and much more. We believe that mental health is a critical issue that affects people of all genders, but men in particular often face unique challenges when seeking help. Limited accessibility to mental health resources, difficulty finding specialized therapists, and stigmas surrounding men's mental health can make it difficult for men to get the help they need. At Men's Therapy Center, we're addressing these challenges head-on to create solutions that make it easier for men to access the mental health care they need. We welcome clients of all backgrounds and identities, including those in the LGBTQ+ community, young men, and children. We're committed to breaking the stigma and making it easy for men to access the help they need. Join us on this journey to better mental health. Learn more at: menstherapycenter.com

Description: The Rental Search Platform for Roommates
Full Description: Gaggle is an innovative online rental property search platform for roommates designed with collaboration and communication at its core. Gaggle provides prospective roommates with a centralized location to share, discuss and compare rental listings. Developed by former roommates, Gaggle knows that everyone has specific criteria for their ideal apartment. Gaggle provides analytic tools to help the group quantify and rank their apartment choices. With Gaggle, roommates are empowered to make an informed, mutually beneficial selection for their next rental. With our platform, users create “Gaggles”; invitation only groups with shared saved listings, customizable notes and image upload capability for each listing. "Note Pad", an in-app message board, is designed to keep thoughts organized and information readily accessible when considering multiple properties. “Gaggle Analytics” provides quantitative metrics to help roommates quickly find and rank rentals based on everyone’s requirements and preferences. The Gaggle user experience incorporates the feel of pre-existing technologies and applies them to the rental property search process. Gaggle provides a more efficient, customizable and intuitive platform focussed on the user.
